description: Evolution AB (publ) develops, produces, markets, and licenses live casino and slots solutions to gaming operators primarily in Europe and the United States. The company runs the game from a casino gaming table, which is streamed in real time and end users make betting decisions on their devices, such as computers, smartphones, tablets, etc. Its portfolio of online live table games primarily includes Live Roulette, Blackjack, Baccarat, Super Sic Bo, Dragon Tiger, Craps, Live Casino Hold'em, Three Card Poker, and Ultimate Texas Hold'em; and operates approximately 1000 tables. The company was formerly known as Evolution Gaming Group AB (publ). Evolution AB (publ) was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
